revisions.description: Rev 1.00.26 J Modules are now part of IP500v2.
Rev 1.00.25 Additional IOD for IP500v2 Select and IP Office Server Edition Expansion Select Mode.
Rev 1.00.24 Additional IOD for IP 500 UCM V2 module
Rev 1.00.23 Update description for Unified Communications Module
Rev 1.00.22 Additional IOD for IP 500 ATM4U V2 module.
Rev 1.00.21 Additional IOD for IP 500 VCM module.
Rev 1.00.20 Additional OID for IP Office Server Edition Expansion Mode.
Rev 1.00.19 Added new C110 UCP Module.
Rev 1.00.18 Added new OID for TCM 8 card.
Rev 1.00.17 Added new OID for DS30A Expansion module.
Rev 1.00.16 Avaya Inside OIDs removed. Additional OIDs added for Norstar, Branch and Quick IP Office modes.
Rev 1.00.15 Added new OID for Combo Card VCM sub module.
Rev 1.00.14 Added new OID for Avaya Inside.
Rev 1.00.13 Added new OIDs for IP500v2, combo card and ETR card.
Rev 1.00.12 Added a new OID for IP500 4 Port Expansion Module.
Rev 1.00.11 Corrected PRI module defined for IP500 and revised description for Ethernet wAN link ports to make common across units.
Rev 1.00.10 Added a new OID for Universal PRI module and revised descriptions for LAN ports used on IP412.
Rev 1.00.09 Added further OIDs for missing modules. Replaced references to IP408 with IP500
Rev 1.00.08 Added new OIDs for IP500 chassis and plug-in cards.
Rev 1.00.07 Added new OID for generic IP Office License dongle.
Rev 1.00.06 Added new OID for revised variant of ATM4U trunk module.
Rev 1.00.05 Corrected descriptions of E1 R2 modules/ports.
Rev 1.00.04 Added new OIDs for revised (v2) variants of DS and POTS expansion modules.
Rev 1.00.03 Added SOG family products.
Rev 1.00.02 Revised for external publication.
Rev 1.0.1 New OIDs added for revised 403 and 406 variants.
Rev 1.0.0 The first published version of this MIB module.
